5\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104okp1665702988873.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/okp1665702988873.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/okp1665702988873.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"okp1665702988873\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Mnemonics for Nonprintable ASCII\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"okp1665702988873__mnemonics_for_nonprintable_ascii_193774\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The control codes required by devices and function key sequences on keyboards often contain nonprintable ASCII characters (with values between 0 and 32 decimal) such as ^ESC, ^SOH, ^NUL, and so on. The translation table compiler recognizes special mnemonics for nonprintable ASCII characters.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"okp1665702988873__p_d64616e1_d64617e1_d64618e1\">When a non-alphanumeric code (such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">clear_screen</code>) is sent to an output device, it expects to receive control codes that represent this function. When a nonalphanumeric key, such as PF1, is pressed, the keyboard sends out a sequence of codes that represent this key.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"okp1665702988873__p_d64619e1_d64620e1_d64621e1\">The documentation that is supplied with the device or keyboard should list the control codes or keyboard code required for these special functions and keys.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"okp1665702988873__p_d64622e1_d64623e1_d64624e1\">Uniface ignores the case of the mnemonics, that is, uppercase and lowercase are equivalent. An optional single caret (^) can be used in front of a mnemonic to improve the readability of a device translation table.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"okp1665702988873__table_d5675e1_d5676e1_d5677e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"okp1665702988873__table_d5675e1_d5676e1_d5677e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"okp1665702988873__table_d5675e1_d5676e1_d5677e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Mnemonic-0-0\" id=\"topic-Mnemonic-0-0\" name=\"topic-Mnemonic-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Mnemonic-0-0\">Mnemonic</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Decimal value-1-0\" id=\"topic-Decimal value-1-0\" name=\"topic-Decimal value-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Decimal value-1-0\">Decimal value</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Octal value-2-0\" id=\"topic-Octal value-2-0\" name=\"topic-Octal value-2-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Octal value-2-0\">Octal value</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-ASCII character-3-0\" id=\"topic-ASCII character-3-0\" name=\"topic-ASCII character-3-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-ASCII character-3-0\">ASCII character</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label><input aria-label=\"Filter results in the table\" class=\"zDocsInputField\" id=\"search-all-smart-table\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><button aria-label=\"Submit\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldSearch\" type=\"submit\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-